V7P3R: V7P3R Chess Engine v6.0 - Advanced Strategic Edition Build Summary ✅ Build Status: SUCCESSFUL Executable Created: V7P3R_v6.0.exe File Size: ~7.8MB (consistent with v5.0/v5.1) UCI Interface: ✅ Working correctly Version String: ✅ "V7P3R v6.0" (corrected from v5.4) 🚀 New Features Implemented in v6.0 1. Advanced Tactical Pattern Recognition Enhanced tactical motif detection (pins, forks, skewers, discovered attacks) Improved tactical scoring in _tactical_pattern_recognition() Better evaluation of tactical opportunities and threats 2. Enhanced Pawn Structure Evaluation Upgraded _enhanced_pawn_structure() replacing legacy _pawn_structure() Advanced passed pawn evaluation with _advanced_passed_pawn_eval() Better understanding of pawn chains, islands, and weaknesses 3. Improved Endgame Logic Comprehensive _endgame_logic() implementation Better king and pawn endgame evaluation Enhanced theoretical knowledge for common endgame patterns 4. Strategic Opening & Capture Guidelines _opening_principles() for better opening play _capture_guidelines() for improved capture evaluation More strategic decision-making in the opening phase 5. Optimized Scoring Calculation Redundancy Cleanup: Removed duplicate/overlapping methods Eliminated redundant _piece_activity() (covered by _mobility_score() and _improved_minor_piece_activity()) Removed duplicate _pawn_structure() calls (replaced by _enhanced_pawn_structure()) Cleaned up _passed_pawns() overlap (integrated into enhanced pawn logic) Fixed _tactical_evaluation() duplication (replaced by _tactical_pattern_recognition()) Bug Fixes: Corrected material scoring to handle string piece type keys properly Performance: More efficient evaluation with cleaner code structure 🔧 Technical Improvements Code Quality Removed redundant method calls from calculate_score() Fixed material scoring piece type mapping Cleaner, more maintainable codebase Better separation of concerns Dependencies Simplified to 4 core files: v7p3r_uci.py (UCI interface) v7p3r.py (main engine) time_manager.py (time management) v7p3r_scoring_calculation.py (evaluation) No external piece square table dependencies Streamlined build process 🎯 Expected Tournament Performance Improvements Better Tactical Awareness
